Package io.manebot.database.search.handler

Interface SearchArgumentHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComparingSearchHandler, SearchHandlerEntityProperty, SearchHandlerPropertyContains, SearchHandlerPropertyEquals, SearchHandlerPropertyIn, SearchHandlerPropertyIsNull, SearchHandlerPropertyNumeric
    public interface SearchArgumentHandler
    Expresses a search argument handler. Search argument handlers are the JPA-level token constructors that build a JPA query from lexically-parsed SearchArguments. These are called by a SearchHandler implementation.
